On the way back the airport, the driver mentioned that the local Supercharger had a line of 50 Teslas waiting to charge after the eclipse.

I hesitate to mention this because then @travisgoodspeed will mock me for having a Tesla.

CISA has released a statement on SQL injection. It just says the same thing we've been saying for 20 years ("use parameterized queries"). Saying this hasn't worked for 20 years, and there's no reason to believe it's going to work because CISA says so.

Getting off the plane, going through immigration, and getting on an Uber took about 5 minutes. I love the efficiency but am depressed by the privacy I’ve sacrificed for it. They don’t even scan my passport on arrival— just facial recognition.

C = chief, you are the leader rather than the doer, you need leadership skills.
O = you are an officer of the organization, you put the needs of the organization first (which is really hard, since most techies put their own agenda's before the organization's).
